                <field id="selectors" translate="label comment" type="textarea" sortOrder="10"
                       showInDefault="1" showInWebsite="1" showInStore="1">
                    <label>Custom Selectors (JSON)</label>
                    <comment><![CDATA[
JSON array of custom selector configurations. Each object supports these fields:<br/>
<strong>label</strong> (string) — A descriptive name for this target.<br/>
<strong>selector</strong> (string, required) — CSS selector of the element to overlay.<br/>
<strong>effect</strong> (string) — shimmer | pulse | wave | static. Default: shimmer.<br/>
<strong>height</strong> (string) — Height in px (e.g. "300px") or "auto". Default: auto.<br/>
<strong>aspect_ratio</strong> (string) — e.g. "16:9". If set, overrides height.<br/>
<strong>border_radius</strong> (string) — In pixels. Default: 0.<br/>
<strong>bg_color</strong> (string) — Hex background color. Default: #e0e0e0.<br/>
<strong>hl_color</strong> (string) — Hex highlight color. Default: #f5f5f5.<br/>
<strong>animation_speed</strong> (string) — In milliseconds. Default: 1500.<br/>
<strong>pages</strong> (string) — Comma-separated page types: home,category,product,cms,all.<br/><br/>
<strong>Example:</strong><br/>
<code>[{"label":"My Custom Slider","selector":".my-slider","effect":"shimmer","height":"300px","aspect_ratio":"","border_radius":"0","bg_color":"#e0e0e0","hl_color":"#f5f5f5","animation_speed":"1500","pages":"home,category"}]</code>
                    ]]></comment>
